Plants coming back are: Camissonia californica, Hirschfeldia incana, Ambrosia acanthicarpa, Schismus barbatus, Erodium cicutarium, Filago californica, F. gallica, Lupinus bicolor, Cryptantha intermedia, Pterostegia drymarioides, Bromus madritensis rubens, Lotus strigosus, Nemophila menziesii, and Chenopodium sp.
